### Calibre PDF Conversion

Calibre's biggest strength is PDF handling. While PDF-to-EPUB is never perfect (PDFs are fixed-layout, EPUBs are reflowable), Calibre's heuristic processing does a better job than almost anything else at extracting clean text from PDFs.

Enable **"OCR the input"** in the conversion settings for scanned PDFs, and Calibre will run Tesseract OCR to extract the text layer.

### Verdict

Download Calibre if you:
- Have PDFs to convert
- Manage a large ebook library
- Need MOBI or AZW3 output for Kindle
- Want a one-time setup that serves you for years

